################################### simple 3D cavity case
reset
###################################### geometry
# {R_inlet = 1/2 }
# {R_outlet = .9202/2 }

brick x 43.9 y 43.9 z 129.9
create Cylinder height 8.05 radius {R_inlet}
create Cylinder height 8.05 radius {R_outlet}

rotate Volume 2 angle 90  about X include_merged 
rotate Volume 3 angle 90  about X include_merged 

move Volume 1 location 0 0 64.95 include_merged 
move Volume 2 location 0 -25.975 30.50725 include_merged 
move Volume 3 location 0 25.975 2.753623 include_merged 

imprint volume all 
merge volume all 
####################################### mesh
# inlet
surface 9  scheme circle 
surface 9 size auto factor 5
mesh surface 9

volume 2  redistribute nodes off 
volume 2  scheme Sweep  source surface 9    target surface 8  sweep transform least squares 
volume 2  autosmooth target off  fixed imprints off  smart smooth off 
volume 2  size auto factor 5
mesh volume 2 
